details.name: Fantasy World 2br, 1001 BnB
details.description:
Welcome to our enchanting vacation home at Fantasy World Villas, the ultimate resort for your Orlando adventure! Situated just minutes from Disney, Universal Studios, and Sea World, this modern and beautifully designed villa offers a delightful Monsters Inc-themed bedroom, exceptional amenities, and easy access to shopping, dining, and attractions.

The House:
Discover the perfect blend of style and comfort in our villa, less than a 3-minute walk from the clubhouse and main pool area. The house features:

A whimsical Monsters Inc-themed double bedroom with two double beds
A luxurious master bedroom with a king-size bed
A fully-equipped kitchen
A laundry room with washer, dryer, iron, and board
Smart TVs with cable in the living room and both bedrooms
A private patio for relaxation and enjoyment
Free WiFi, parking, and resort access

The Resort:
Fantasy World Villas offers a spectacular array of amenities for guests of all ages, including:

Daily scheduled activities for kids and adults
Two large heated pools and three hot tubs
Heated Lazy River
Two water slides (48" height requirement)
Tiki bar, 
Arcade room, 
Gym, 
Kid's splash pad
Outdoor fireplace 
Electric car chargers
Children's playground, 
Charcoal grills, gas grills, and picnic tables
Tennis, pickleball, basketball, and a batting cage for softball & baseball
Sand volleyball court, shuffleboard, and bocce ball
Scheduled transportation to Walt Disney World, Universal Studios, and Sea World (currently $5 per person for round trip).

With its prime location, unique decor, and fantastic resort amenities, our villa at Fantasy World Villas is the ideal destination for your magical Orlando getaway. Immerse yourself in the excitement of the theme parks and create lasting memories with your loved ones. Book your stay today!.

details.name: Fantasy World 2br, 1020 BnB
details.description:
Welcome to our enchanting villa at Fantasy World Villas, the ultimate resort destination just minutes from Disney, Universal Studios, and Sea World. Immerse yourself in a dream vacation in this modernly designed 2-bedroom home offering comfort, style, and convenience.

Situated right by the sports courts and a large picnic area, our villa is only a short 2-minute walk from the main pool area, waterslides, and clubhouse. The delightful double bedroom features a charming Disney's Mickey theme with two double beds, while the master bedroom boasts a luxurious king-size bed. Smart TVs with cable are available in the living room and both bedrooms.

Enjoy the fully-equipped kitchen and laundry room with a washer, dryer, iron, and ironing board. Step onto the private patio to relax and soak in the beautiful surroundings. Free Wi-Fi, parking, and resort access are included.

The resort offers an impressive array of amenities and activities for all ages, including daily scheduled activities, heated pools, hot tubs, lazy river, water slides (48" height requirement), tiki bar, arcade room, gym, kid's splash pad, outdoor fireplace, electric car chargers, playground, grills and picnic tables, tennis, pickleball, basketball, batting cage, sand volleyball, shuffleboard, and bocce ball.

Scheduled transportation to major attractions is available at $5 per person (round trip). The villa is within walking distance to popular restaurants and just 1 mile from Walmart, Publix, and other grocery stores.

Book our magical villa at Fantasy World Villas today for an unforgettable vacation experience!

details.name: Lake Berkley 4br, 946 Park Terrace
details.description:
Welcome to our stunning 4-bedroom family retreat, nestled within the exclusive Lake Berkley Resort - a premier gated community with 24-hour security. Designed to accommodate families and groups of all sizes, our home is just minutes away from world-famous attractions like Disney, Universal Studios, and Sea World. Moreover, it's conveniently situated within an hour's drive from Legoland, pristine Atlantic Ocean and Gulf Coast beaches, and other captivating attractions.

Our spacious home can comfortably host up to 10 guests, providing the perfect blend of modern design, comfort, and convenience. The open living room offers seating for 8 guests, while the dining area accommodates 6. The breakfast bar provides seating for an additional 3 guests. The laundry room is fully equipped with a washer, dryer, iron, and board for your convenience.

With 3.5 well-appointed bathrooms, high chair, pack and play, safety gates, and TVs in every bedroom, we've ensured that all guests, including the little ones, are well catered for. All beds feature ultra-comfortable memory foam mattresses, promising a restful night's sleep.

The first floor boasts a large master suite with a king-size bed and luxurious design. Upstairs, the second master suite offers a private balcony overlooking the resort, a king-size bed, and an opulent design. The third bedroom is a Star Wars-themed haven, complete with a bunk bed (twin size on top and bottom), and wall-to-wall decorations to fully immerse you in the action. Lastly, the fourth bedroom is a magical Disney's Frozen-themed sanctuary, featuring two cozy twin-XL beds..

Just a short walk from the house, you'll find the resort's pool area, gym, clubhouse, grills, and picnic tables. Lake Berkley Resort offers a range of fantastic amenities, including a serene lake with a walking path, picturesque views of the Florida landscape, breathtaking sunsets, a fishing deck, outdoor exercise equipment, a children's playground, and much more.

In the vicinity of the house, you'll find a Walmart and Aldi within a mile, as well as local shops and restaurants. Nearby attractions include Gatorland, swamp airboat rides, safari rides, mini-golf, and dinner shows like Medieval Times (less than 1 mile away).

Experience the ultimate Florida getaway at our beautifully-appointed Lake Berkley Resort home - an oasis of relaxation and excitement for the entire family. Book now for a memorable vacation!
